Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.60,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女不可能每次都会通知鸫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想阻止她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得地狱少女挺好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被送下地狱的都是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.30,0:02:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子姐姐和地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村井叔叔的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.00,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}和蔼的邻居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.60,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来今年没来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.60,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年来过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说那是他们家田里收上来的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.40,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 又喝成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝了 不喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了回家吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 那是什么花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是彼岸花吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼岸花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村井前辈 村井前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.00,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再来点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情好些了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满以为田里的收成一定也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能告诉我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是两年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.80,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚搬来这里时的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人叫关根良介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在田地的另一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为曾经在出版社工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人总不是太信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这里我们不太受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇上了很多很多苦头 现在戒酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.60,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你辞职下地真是很坚定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得从爷爷那继承了那么大一片地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不种些什么就太浪费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妻子去世之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子一直很孤单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的话　我想就能多在一起些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会种菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是门外汉 可能不会那么简单就成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们决定了两个人一起努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我可能可以帮上你们一点忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前种过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不知道能不能帮上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 优子 叔叔肯帮我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来那个人开始 每天都来我们家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从犁地到选种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么撒水到怎么施肥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常耐心地教我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了镇上我们都被看做外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.10,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对爸爸来说他是唯一的聊天伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了他的帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.50,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在最困难的第一年也种出了美味的蔬菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.30,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在都记得 那天的爸爸非常高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.30,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上他说服了颇有微辞的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬是扩大了田地的范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年由于天气异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫害非常严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关根先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前撒上农药就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没有那个能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不作出点损失无法渡过这个难关啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,农药很贵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把以前家里用的分给你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气 我们加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.10,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然爸爸相信了他的话每天撒农药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜却逐渐都枯萎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的爸爸又开始喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是再问问看其他人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去真的会都枯萎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.30,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 只要照关根先生说的做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.20,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终爸爸没有找任何人而是一直等着农药起效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里误闯进来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 喝了那东西的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么是能杀死害虫的农药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把掺了水的果汁给了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.70,0:11:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他的企图 爸爸相信那是真的农药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个人要怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来我听说了才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和死去的爷爷为了这块地吵过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是报复吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爸爸一定要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬到新家 开始了新工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想过平常的生活而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就登录了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到了一个稻草人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳子就能为你复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很理解优子的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不能复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫你不要说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果解开绳子 有一个人就会下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说这样也许能复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.60,0:12:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你送一个人下地狱的事实将永远无法抹去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就必须一生背负着这个事实活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多痛苦的事你知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解你父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是喜欢谈论你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只考虑你的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲一定不希望你帮他复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.80,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要说为了他而一生背负罪孽这种事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像情况变得不妙了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我来保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.10,0:13:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做太过分了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能收回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.90,0:15:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能那样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬抢太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能确实很卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过请你理解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望优子去复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子姐姐的爸爸不就是被那个人给害死的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生里会发生很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面会有难以置信的事 没有道理的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但必须跨越过那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被杀也无所谓吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你帮那种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送下地狱不是活该的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.20,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子姐姐的爸爸什么坏事都没有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人快点死了就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一真是个不懂情理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一被杀了的话 我也会复仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.30,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.60,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫会说那种话还是我的错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.50,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好 我不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是要由你自己抉择的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.80,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有他无法原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到鸫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿都找不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去那 晚上很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.70,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.00,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸫的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.00,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.00,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 你知道我多担心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大的雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.90,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有说担心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.30,0:19:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 让人这么担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的让我担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不复仇了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把握住幸福的生活哦 连你父亲的那份一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我会努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢一而再地妨碍我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底还是没让你出场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然对那个男人得想点办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 不过我想再在这里待一阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有很多和父亲在一起的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这里为抵押借了钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭据都好好地在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.50,0:21:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了扩田可是花了很多钱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不要这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他说不行一定要抵给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做那么卑鄙的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样你才会满意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.30,0:21:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他一直到最后都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你 你还算是个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.90,0:21:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微变干净点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能卖个好价钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.70,0:22:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是解开绳子好些吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样优子姐姐就能一直留在那房子里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.60,0:22:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是阿一不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.70,0:22:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心的 马上就会有新朋友的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.20,0:22:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.70,0:23:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是要由你自己抉择的事
