Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.80,0:24:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些忘不掉的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.90,0:24:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些抹不去的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.10,0:24:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 我还没把一切告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.60,0:24:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是请你理解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.40,0:24:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.50,0:24:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.50,0:24:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得复仇不是件坏事
